| Feature           | `close()`     | `quit()`          |
| ----------------- | ------------- | ----------------- |
| Kills 1 tab only  | âœ…             | âŒ                 |
| Ends full session | âŒ             | âœ…                 |
| Frees memory      | âŒ (partial)   | âœ… (full)          |
| Safe in loops     | âœ… (with care) | âŒ (donâ€™t overuse) |
| After final test  | âŒ             | âœ…                 |

